

                       ************* Angular basic commands and steps ******************
                
                
    **** declaration component while lazy loading and loading and writing route in respective component is important ***
                
                
1. Create new project :  ng new project_name

2. create component : ng g c component_name 

3. Show component in root app :
       
       [i]   app module imports component in app.module.ts (autmatic by cli)
       [ii]  component selector add to component html file

4. Create module :
       [i] ng g m modulename 

5. show to app :
        [i] export **components** from new_module.module.ts
        [ii]  import **new_module** in app.module.ts
        [iii] add component selectors to apps html file
        
6. Root level routes :

       [i] component 1
       [ii] component 2
       [iii] import components in app-routes
       [iv]  route [
                     {  
                        path:"component 1(exp. user)",
                        component:Imported_component_name
                     },
                     {  
                        path:"component 1(exp. user)",
                        component:Imported_component_name
                     }  
                        ]
                        
        [v]   add anchor tag and ->  routerLink="path"
        [vi]  add <router-outlet></router-outlet>
        
        
        
7. Generate module level routing
       ng g m module_name --routing
                     
                     
8. Lazy loading import module add app-route:
       {
       path:'admin' ,loadChilder:()=>import('./admin/admin.module')	
       .then(mod=>mod.AdminModule)	
       }


9. Generate module and routing inside component 
      ng g m component/ImgclassificationTest --routing
      
      
      
