"""
}


14. sessions:


sessions are two types 1. local storage 2. web storage

local storage data will not be delated and available for next day month or year. Accessible only at client side. Avalibale for all pager undeer same domain

component.ts==>
ngoninit(){
localStorage.setItem('key','value')
sessionStorage.setItem('key','value')

console.log(localStorage.getItem("key")
console.log(sessionStorage.getItem("key")

}

sessionstorage :
delete data on delete tab.



ref : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3220660/local-storage-vs-cookies
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
